%% Sequence Diagram: Complete FYP System - Multi-Agent Story Generation
%% Shows complete message flow across all iterations including future features

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant StoryAgent
    participant Director as DirectorAgent
    participant Prompt as PromptAgent
    participant Writer as WriterAgent
    participant Reviewer as ReviewerAgent
    participant Editor as EditorAgent
    participant Image as ImageAgent
    participant TTS as TTSAgent
    participant STT as STTAgent
    participant Chatbot as ChatbotAgent
    participant Ollama
    participant SD as Stable Diffusion
    participant Coqui as Coqui TTS
    participant Whisper as OpenAI Whisper

    Note over User,Whisper: Complete FYP System Workflow

    User->>Frontend: 1. Enter prompt & select options
    activate Frontend
    Frontend->>API: 2. POST /api/generate<br/>{prompt, generate_images, generate_audio, mode}
    activate API
    
    API->>StoryAgent: 3. generate_story(prompt, options)
    activate StoryAgent
    StoryAgent->>Director: 4. create_story(prompt, options)
    activate Director
    
    Note over Director,Prompt: Step 1: Advanced Prompt Processing
    Director->>Prompt: 5. process_prompt(user_prompt)
    activate Prompt
    Prompt->>Ollama: 6. Validate, enhance & classify prompt
    Ollama-->>Prompt: Enhanced prompt + classification
    Prompt->>Prompt: 7. Detect language & age group
    Prompt-->>Director: 8. (enhanced_prompt, type, language, age_group)
    deactivate Prompt
    
    Note over Director,Writer: Step 2: Intelligent Story Generation
    Director->>Writer: 9. generate_story(enhanced_prompt, context)
    activate Writer
    Writer->>Ollama: 10. Generate story with character development
    Ollama-->>Writer: JSON story with rich characters
    Writer->>Writer: 11. Create character backstories
    Writer-->>Director: 12. (story_dict, "Story generated ✅")
    deactivate Writer
    
    Note over Director,Reviewer: Step 3: Comprehensive Quality Review
    Director->>Reviewer: 13. review_story(story_dict)
    activate Reviewer
    Reviewer->>Ollama: 14. Validate content, coherence & age-appropriateness
    Ollama-->>Reviewer: Detailed validation feedback
    Reviewer->>Reviewer: 15. Check educational value
    Reviewer-->>Director: 16. (reviewed_story, "Review complete ✅")
    deactivate Reviewer
    
    Note over Director,Editor: Step 4: Professional Editing & Export
    Director->>Editor: 17. edit_story(reviewed_story)
    activate Editor
    Editor->>Editor: 18. Polish text & apply style guide
    Editor->>Editor: 19. Generate PDF with illustrations
    Editor->>Editor: 20. Format for publication
    Editor-->>Director: 21. (final_story, "Edit complete ✅")
    deactivate Editor
    
    Director-->>StoryAgent: 22. {story, status, outputs}
    deactivate Director
    StoryAgent-->>API: 23. (result, status_string)
    deactivate StoryAgent
    
    Note over API,Image: Step 5: Advanced Image Generation (if enabled)
    loop For each scene with character consistency
        API->>Image: 24. generate_image(scene_desc, character_refs, filename)
        activate Image
        Image->>SD: 25. txt2img with character consistency
        SD-->>Image: Low-res image
        Image->>SD: 26. img2img hires fix with style transfer
        SD-->>Image: High-res consistent image
        Image->>Image: 27. Apply upscaling & style transfer
        Image-->>API: 28. image_path
        deactivate Image
    end
    
    Note over API,TTS: Step 6: Audio Generation (if enabled)
    alt Audio Generation Enabled
        loop For each scene
            API->>TTS: 29. generate_audio(scene_text, voice_style)
            activate TTS
            TTS->>Coqui: 30. Synthesize speech with emotion
            Coqui-->>TTS: Audio file with voice effects
            TTS-->>API: 31. audio_path
            deactivate TTS
        end
    end
    
    Note over API,Chatbot: Step 7: Interactive Features (if enabled)
    alt Chatbot Mode Enabled
        API->>Chatbot: 32. Initialize conversation context
        activate Chatbot
        Chatbot->>Ollama: 33. Prepare conversational AI
        Ollama-->>Chatbot: Context ready
        Chatbot-->>API: 34. Chatbot ready for interaction
        deactivate Chatbot
    end
    
    API->>API: 35. Add all URLs to story
    API->>API: 36. Save final story JSON with metadata
    
    Note over API: Step 8: Background Evaluation & Learning
    API->>EvaluationAgent: 37. Spawn subprocess (non-blocking)
    API->>API: 38. Update user preferences & learning
    
    API-->>Frontend: 39. {status, story with all media URLs, chatbot_ready}
    deactivate API
    
    Frontend->>Frontend: 40. Parse story & prepare display
    Frontend->>Frontend: 41. Initialize audio players & chatbot
    
    alt Interactive Mode
        Frontend-->>User: 42. Show story with audio, chatbot & navigation
        User->>Frontend: 43. Voice input or chat interaction
        Frontend->>STT: 44. Process voice input
        STT->>Whisper: 45. Transcribe speech
        Whisper-->>STT: Text transcription
        STT-->>Frontend: 46. Transcribed text
        Frontend->>API: 47. Send chat message
        API->>Chatbot: 48. Process user input
        Chatbot->>Ollama: 49. Generate response
        Ollama-->>Chatbot: Response text
        Chatbot-->>API: 50. Chat response
        API-->>Frontend: 51. Chat response
        Frontend-->>User: 52. Display chat response
    else Standard Mode
        Frontend-->>User: 53. Show story with page navigation & audio
    end
    
    deactivate Frontend

